sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant W as WebView (React)
    participant R as Rust Backend
    participant B as Browser
    participant API as Provider API

    Note over U,API: Codex / Gemini / Antigravity (PKCE OAuth)
    U->>W: "Connect Provider" 클릭
    W->>R: invoke('auth_connect', { provider })
    R->>R: hyper 로컬 HTTP 콜백 서버 시작
    R->>R: pkce.rs → code_verifier + challenge (S256)
    R->>B: open::that(OAuth URL)
    B->>U: 로그인 페이지
    U->>B: 로그인 완료
    B->>R: localhost callback → auth code
    R->>API: auth code + code_verifier → tokens
    API-->>R: access_token + refresh_token
    R->>R: keyring에 토큰 저장
    R->>W: emit("auth:connected")

    Note over U,API: GitHub Copilot (Device Flow)
    U->>W: "Connect Copilot" 클릭
    W->>R: invoke('auth_connect', { provider: 'copilot' })
    R->>API: POST /login/device/code
    API-->>R: device_code + user_code
    R->>W: emit("auth:device-code", user_code)
    W->>U: "github.com/login/device에서 코드 입력"
    U->>B: 코드 입력
    loop Polling
        R->>API: POST /login/oauth/access_token
    end
    API-->>R: gho_xxx token
    R->>API: POST /copilot_internal/v2/token
    API-->>R: copilot_token (30min TTL)
    R->>R: keyring에 저장
    R->>W: emit("auth:connected")

    Note over U,API: Claude (Setup Token)
    U->>W: Setup Token 입력
    W->>R: invoke('auth_connect', { provider: 'claude', token })
    R->>API: setup_token → access_token + refresh_token
    API-->>R: tokens
    R->>R: keyring에 저장
    R->>W: emit("auth:connected")

    Note over U,API: 채팅 메시지 전송
    U->>W: 메시지 입력 + 전송
    W->>R: invoke('chat_send', { convId, msg, provider })
    R->>API: SSE 스트리밍 요청 (reqwest + eventsource-stream)
    loop Token Streaming
        API-->>R: chunk
        R->>W: emit("chat:stream", chunk)
        W->>U: 실시간 렌더링
    end
    R->>R: rusqlite에 저장
    R->>W: emit("chat:complete")
